         <div>
            <head>Translated parts</head>
            <p xml:id="KR2e0003-start">
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_131-1a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-13T19:56:12.735+09:00">                                    Having done so he gave his companions a flagon of wine.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_148-2a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-16T23:11:49.083+09:00">Longsword, let us return!</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_470-1a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T23:41:50.548+09:00">                                    'Good' said the king,</seg>
            <seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_456-5a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#wilke" modified="2020-06-23T01:26:57.011+09:00">The king said: "How could it be that a minister offends someone by exhausting his strength</seg><seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_456-5a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#wilke" modified="2020-06-23T01:26:58.672+09:00">and using up his abilities?"</seg><seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_456-5a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#wilke" modified="2020-06-23T01:33:54.68+09:00">Su Dai replied: "Please let me make a comparison for Your Majesty.</seg><seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_456-5a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#wilke" modified="2020-06-23T01:40:33.021+09:00">In the past, the following once occurred in the upper regions of Zhou.</seg><seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_456-5a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#wilke" modified="2020-06-23T01:46:24.539+09:00">A certain husband served as an official [in a faraway place] and had not returned home for three years,</seg><seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_456-5a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#wilke" modified="2020-06-23T01:48:09.301+09:00">so his wife was having an affair with someone else.</seg><seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_456-5a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#wilke" modified="2020-06-23T01:49:46.886+09:00">Her lover said:</seg><seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_456-5a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#wilke" modified="2020-06-23T01:52:32.919+09:00">'When your husband returns,</seg><seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_456-5a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#wilke" modified="2020-06-23T01:52:40.371+09:00">what are we going to do?'</seg><seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_456-5a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#wilke" modified="2020-06-23T01:57:02.17+09:00">The wife in question replied: "Don't worry,</seg><seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_456-5a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#wilke" modified="2020-06-23T02:01:02+09:00">I have already prepared poisoned wine and wait for his return."</seg><seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_456-5a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#wilke" modified="2020-06-23T20:06:34.08+09:00">After some time, her husband did indeed return,</seg><seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_456-5a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#wilke" modified="2020-06-23T20:15:00.754+09:00">whereupon she ordered his concubine to ladle the poisoned wine and present it to him.</seg><seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_456-5a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#wilke" modified="2020-06-23T20:16:22.772+09:00">His concubine knew about the plan</seg><seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_456-5a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#wilke" modified="2020-06-23T20:16:28.807+09:00">and stopped half way.</seg><seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_456-5a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#wilke" modified="2020-06-23T20:19:38.485+09:00">She thought:</seg><seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_456-5a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#wilke" modified="2020-06-23T20:24:59.061+09:00">"If I give my master this to drink,</seg><seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_456-5a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#wilke" modified="2020-06-23T20:25:13.511+09:00">then it will kill him.</seg><seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_456-5a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#wilke" modified="2020-06-23T20:29:54.491+09:00">If I tell my master about this matter,</seg><seg corresp="#KR2e0003_tls_456-5a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#wilke" modified="2020-06-23T20:30:02.275+09:00">he will banish my mistress.</seg></p>
